org.osate.xtext.aadl2.errormodel.errorModel

Interface ErrorModelSubclause

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AnnexSubclause, AObject, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, ModalElement, NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ErrorModelSubclauseImpl

    public interface ErrorModelSubclause
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, AnnexSubclause
    A representation of the model object 'Subclause'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Propagation
    • Component Behavior
    • Composite Behavior
    • Observable Propagation Connections
    • Connection Transformation
    • Properties
